1.Reverse a String

Method 1:

a="python is  a easy language"
b=''
for word in a[::-1]:
    b=b+word
print(b)


Method 2:
a="python is  a easy language"
ad=a
b=''
for word in a[::-1]:
    b=b+word
if b==ad:
    print("palindrome:",b)
else:
    print("not a palindrome:",b)



2. pre pend method for rev string

Method 1:
a="python is a language"
clean=a.replace(" ","").lower()
rev_str=""
for word in a:
    rev_str=word+rev_str
print(rev_str)


